  "text": "Found 6 deprecated classes in the Apache Flink DataStream API (flink-streaming-java/src):\n\n1. AscendingTimestampExtractor (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/functions/timestamps/AscendingTimestampExtractor.java) - A deprecated timestamp extractor for streams with monotonously ascending timestamps. No replacement is explicitly documented in the javadoc.\n\n2. TextInputFormat (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextInputFormat.java) - A deprecated I/O format class for reading text files. The javadoc recommends using FLIP-27 FileSource instead as the replacement.\n\n3. TextOutputFormat (flink-streaming-java/src/main/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/api/legacy/io/TextOutputFormat.java) - A deprecated I/O format class for writing text files. The javadoc recommends using Sink-V2 FlinkSink instead as the replacement.\n\n4. OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java) - A deprecated test harness for testing OneInputStreamTask. The javadoc recommends using StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder instead.\n\n5. StreamTaskTestHarness (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/StreamTaskTestHarness.java) - A deprecated test harness for testing StreamTask. The javadoc recommends using StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder instead.\n\n6. TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness (flink-streaming-java/src/test/java/org/apache/flink/streaming/runtime/tasks/TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness.java) - A deprecated test harness for testing TwoInputStreamTask. The javadoc recommends using StreamTaskMailboxTestHarness and StreamTaskMailboxTestHarnessBuilder instead.\n\nThe deprecated classes fall into the following categories:\n- Timestamp extractors: AscendingTimestampExtractor\n- I/O format classes: TextInputFormat, TextOutputFormat\n- Test harnesses: OneInputStreamTaskTestHarness, StreamTaskTestHarness, TwoInputStreamTaskTestHarness"
